span> 標題：季拉（gerah）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： גֵּרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： gerah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:13\">EXO 30:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:25\">LEV 27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:47\">NUM 3:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:16\">NUM 18:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:12\">EZK 45:12</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在所有這些經文中，<em>gerah</em> （季拉）只是用來定義舍客勒，1季拉為1舍客勒的1/20；意思是說，<em>gerah</em> 離了舍客勒就沒有意義。如果譯文保留了「舍客勒」，則可同時保留「季拉」。如果「舍客勒」在譯文中換算成了其他單位，翻譯者仍然可以保留「季拉」一詞，稱其為譯文中「舍客勒」對應單位的1/20即可。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
