span> 標題：比加（beqa）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בֶּקַע</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： beqa‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:26\">EXO 38:26</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>根據<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:26\">EXO 38:26</a> ，<em>beqa‘</em> （比加）為半舍客勒。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a> 指出這是一個金鼻環的重量。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 將其換算為舍客勒，英文意為「一個重半舍客勒的金鼻環」。1比加等於10季拉。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
